{"tid":1292250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請置頂] 請給我一首歌的時間去為香港人打氣","createTime":"2019-07-07T08:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:03:46.000Z","uid":1806,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42eeafc8a898095a71ee0d458e9d4c9c2d157dee","tid":1292250,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"我們文宣巴絲整了一段長一首歌既時間既短片為香港人打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mvUu7f1qZQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmvUu7f1qZQk&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=5699648d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mvUu7f1qZQk</a><br />\n香港人過了不平凡的六月<br />\n踏入七月，雖然面對不同的困難，我們香港人記住齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，毋忘五大訴求。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n－ 撤回修訂條例<br />\n－ 追究警隊濫權<br />\n－ 收回暴動定性 <br />\n－ 實行雙真普選<br />\n－ 撤銷義士控罪<br />\n<br />\n香港加油，永不放棄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得累的時候，睇下我地整既打氣片，俾我地去為疲倦既你叉叉電。<br />\n同時也可以離一離開手機，和身邊的朋友傾訴下。<br />\n<br />\n大家繼續努力！Fight For Hong Kong！<br />\n<br />\nCredit to:<br />\nBackground Music - I'll be there by 陳詩慧, Eva Chan<br />\nPictures - TG@文宣組反送中印刷犒件大合集, FB PAGE @喂我喺度呀<br />\n已知有版權的圖同背景歌，已直接聯絡當事人得到許可。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲記者傳媒轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果覺得幾好，請幫我地推POST支持。<br />\n再次多謝各位支持和幫助香港的同路人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d678bdddd618349889e4290511783a201c633458","tid":1292250,"uid":